577
00:35:44,327 --> 00:35:47,647
Right. If Sugyeong's okay, Taesu would be, too.

578
00:35:49,797 --> 00:35:54,057
Did Sugyeong do anything to you?

579
00:35:54,056 --> 00:35:56,996
No, she was very classy.

580
00:35:56,996 --> 00:35:58,866
Sugyeong?

581
00:36:01,226 --> 00:36:03,916
She never once raised her voice.

582
00:36:03,916 --> 00:36:06,067
Sugyeong?

583
00:36:06,067 --> 00:36:07,297
Actually...

584
00:36:07,297 --> 00:36:12,007
