591
00:36:47,246 --> 00:36:49,007
What do you want to tell me?

592
00:36:49,996 --> 00:36:53,626
I respect you very much.

593
00:36:56,067 --> 00:36:59,956
Yes, using flattery before offering a deal,

594
00:36:59,956 --> 00:37:01,797
