595
00:37:02,297 --> 00:37:04,077
No, I'm not trying to offer a deal.

596
00:37:04,077 --> 00:37:06,227
I really do respect you.

597
00:37:06,606 --> 00:37:09,157
You've been dedicated to mom all your life.

598
00:37:09,916 --> 00:37:13,027
She's my mom, so I don't understand why,

599
00:37:13,027 --> 00:37:15,606
but I respect your taste in women.

600
00:37:15,606 --> 00:37:19,257
Anyway, thank you for staying with mom.

601
00:37:23,237 --> 00:37:28,456
And I'm trying to date a woman like her.

602
00:37:30,686 --> 00:37:34,067
I know I made a big mistake.

603
00:37:34,067 --> 00:37:36,447
And I know you're very angry about that.

604
00:37:36,447 --> 00:37:40,277
But it was my fault, not Eunsu's, father.

605
00:37:43,927 --> 00:37:48,817
