606
00:37:49,597 --> 00:37:54,437
Do you have any respect for me?

607
00:37:54,436 --> 00:37:55,956
Of course, I do.

608
00:37:55,956 --> 00:37:57,666
The respect I have for you,

609
00:37:57,666 --> 00:37:59,846
