614
00:38:12,887 --> 00:38:14,737
Tell me the reason.

615
00:38:16,237 --> 00:38:18,856
Every decision I make is to

616
00:38:18,856 --> 00:38:22,326
protect everything I built.

617
00:38:22,327 --> 00:38:25,257
My house, my company,

618
00:38:25,257 --> 00:38:29,217
