674
00:41:52,126 --> 00:41:55,226
She's not interested in me at all.

675
00:41:55,956 --> 00:41:57,326
Excuse me?

676
00:41:58,327 --> 00:42:02,017
She's relying on me only because there's

677
00:42:02,016 --> 00:42:04,496
