703
00:43:38,496 --> 00:43:41,567
How could you not find anything yet?

704
00:43:41,567 --> 00:43:45,016
When I got you all those documents?

705
00:43:45,016 --> 00:43:49,016
No wonder Mr. Jang was confident about them.

706
00:43:49,016 --> 00:43:50,656
What about the stockholders?

707
00:43:50,657 --> 00:43:54,146
Did you find the stockholders from the past?

708
00:43:54,146 --> 00:43:57,086
Actually, we found something strange.

709
00:43:57,086 --> 00:43:58,306
Strange?

710
00:43:58,306 --> 00:44:00,196
There was a major investor when Best Global

711
00:44:00,197 --> 00:44:03,247
was founded, but no one knows his identity.

712
00:44:03,746 --> 00:44:06,536
He bought Taehu Industry at the verge of

713
00:44:06,536 --> 00:44:08,976
