714
00:44:08,976 --> 00:44:10,777
but he resigned after just one year,

715
00:44:10,777 --> 00:44:12,847
and nobody knows where he is now.

716
00:44:12,847 --> 00:44:13,827
We looked for him,

717
00:44:13,827 --> 00:44:17,427
but his address and phone number were fake.

718
00:44:17,427 --> 00:44:20,257
The president when the company was founded

719
00:44:20,257 --> 00:44:22,726
