720
00:44:23,617 --> 00:44:29,897
So where did the investment come from?

721
00:44:31,376 --> 00:44:37,916
I can't help feeling suspicious of Mr. Jang.

722
00:44:38,597 --> 00:44:43,217
There seems to be a problem at Best Global.

723
00:44:43,217 --> 00:44:45,206
